import React from 'react';
import styled from "styled-components";
import {FlexWrapper} from "../../../components/FlexWrapper";
import {Icon} from "../../../components/icon/Icon";
import {ContactForm} from "./form/ContactForm";

export const Contact = () => {
    return (
        <StyledContact>
            <FlexWrapper>
                <FlexWrapper direction={'column'}>
                <ContactHeader>Connect with me:</ContactHeader>
                    <SocialList>
                        <SocialItem>
                            <SocialLink>
                                <Icon iconId={'telegram'} width={'40px'} viewBox={'0 0 40px 40px'} height={'40px'}/>
                            </SocialLink>
                        </SocialItem>
                        <SocialItem>
                            <SocialLink>
                                <Icon iconId={'face'}  width={'40px'} viewBox={'0 0 21px 21px'} height={'40px'}/>
                            </SocialLink>
                        </SocialItem>
                        <SocialItem>
                            <SocialLink>
                                <Icon iconId={'git'} width={'40px'} height={'40px'}/>
                            </SocialLink>
                        </SocialItem>
                        <SocialItem>
                            <SocialLink>
                                <Icon iconId={'git'} width={'40px'} height={'40px'}/>
                            </SocialLink>
                        </SocialItem>
                    </SocialList>
                </FlexWrapper>
            </FlexWrapper>
            <ContactForm/>
        </StyledContact>
    );
};

const StyledContact = styled.section`
  display: flex;
`
const ContactHeader = styled.h2`

`

const SocialList = styled.ul`
  display: flex;
  gap: 30px;

`
const SocialItem = styled.li`

`
const SocialLink = styled.a`

`
